<p>We may disclose your identity to any third party who claims that any content posted or uploaded by you to this site constitutes a violation of their intellectual property rights, or of their right to privacy. Information collected from the Site may also be transferred as part of a merger or sale or as part of a restructuring, bankruptcy or transfer of assets to our successors in interest.&nbsp;</p>
